sequenceDiagram
  participant W as Writer
  participant F as Stream file<br/>(page cache)
  participant L as Sharded WAL
  participant R as Live readers

  W->>F: append — write once into page cache
  F->>L: stage record into WAL
  F-->>R: publish tail, wake readers (memory latency)
  Note over L: group-commit — concurrent appends<br/>from many streams batch into one fsync
  L-->>W: 2xx (only after durable)
